        <item>
            <title>0.1.11</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 11:04:16 +0200</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>0.1.11</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.1.11</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<style>:root{color-scheme:light dark}body{font:14px/1.65 -apple-system,system-ui,sans-serif;color:#1d2122;margin:0;padding:16px 18px}h2{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 12px}ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px}li{margin:6px 0}li::marker{color:#f9a600}@media (prefers-color-scheme:dark){body{color:#e7e9ea}}</style>
<h2>What's new in 0.1.11</h2><ul>
<li>SEO structural fixes now apply instantly and reliably. Open Graph, Twitter cards, canonical URLs, theme color, JSON-LD, sitemap and robots are written straight into your project by the app, so they actually land every time instead of being skipped.</li>
<li>The score updates in real time as fixes apply. Content fixes (titles, descriptions, alt text) still use the agent.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
